7 An Act relating to public finance; imposing
requirements with respect to certain shares;
8 prohibiting actions with respect to advice provided
by proxy advisers without certain commitment;
9 prohibiting grant of proxy voting rights; providing
exceptions; requiring tabulation of certain proxy
10 votes; requiring report to the State Treasurer;
defining term; providing for codification; providing
11 an effective date; and declaring an emergency.
